Accurate and up-to-date information:
Make sure Facebook always shows the right info about your friends and family. This helps you find the people you're looking for with the most recent details.

Flexibility:
Facebook should be easy to use in the way you want. It should work well and find your friends the way you like.

Compliance:
Facebook needs to follow the rules and laws. It should do things the right way and follow what the law says.

User-friendly interface:
Facebook should be simple and easy for you to use. You should be able to do what you want on Facebook without any trouble.
